{
  "stem": "12413.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then at night of September 22nd, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think this was on Yom Kippur day, and the Day of Atonement.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you asked the question of why the Final Solution happened on this very day in every place in Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was done because the Germans wanted to prove to the Jews that they are rejected by  their God.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was true, tragically, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A 12 o'clock at night, the ghetto lit up like a Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They-- there was a Jewish police-- volunteers who did it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I did not know why they did it-- but they collaborated with the German hoping to save their lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would say to save their skin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They lost their soul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were ordered to takes bundles of 20 kilograms-- something like this, no more than that-- and to leave everything intact and to go to a place where there was like an old market.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was done street-by-street, because 30,000 Jews in one day was very hard to-- to cope with this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everything was done with a precision.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything was planned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like a military operation in a way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came to this point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The market was surrounded by SS troops, by Lithuanians, and Latvians-- SS volunteers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a group of high-ranking officers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the one who was in charge of the selection Was an SS captain by the name Degenhart, Degenhart, D-E-G-E-N-H-A-R-T.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Degen means sword in English-- Degenhart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But this was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was a short guy-- custom-made uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He had a scar on his face; black, small eyes-- piercings eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Very arrogant-- wearing white gloves; holding in his right hand a short swagger stick.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
